    <section class="geschichte" id="geschichte">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Unsere Geschichte</h2>
            <p>Mehr als 60 Jahre Leidenschaft für den Unterwassersport</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item fade-in">
                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-header"><span class="timeline-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="3"/><path d="M5 22c0-5 3-7 7-7s7 2 7 7"/><path d="M5 12h14" stroke="#FFD400"/></svg></span><span class="timeline-year">1961</span></div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Gründung des DUC Essen</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">Eine Gruppe begeisterter Taucher gründet den Deutschen Unterwasserclub Essen e.V. und legt den Grundstein für über 60 Jahre Vereinsgeschichte.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item fade-in">
                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-header"><span class="timeline-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M8 13h8" stroke="#FFD400"/><path d="M8 17h8" stroke="#FFD400"/></svg></span><span class="timeline-year">1980er</span></div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Etablierung im VDST</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">Der Verein etabliert sich als feste Größe im Verband Deutscher Sporttaucher und bildet die ersten eigenen Tauchlehrer aus.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item fade-in">
                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-header"><span class="timeline-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FFD400" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5C6 4 6 5.5 6 5.5V9zm12 0h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5C18 4 18 5.5 18 5.5V9z"/><path d="M4 22h16v-4H4z"/><path d="M6 18V9h12v9"/><path d="M12 4v5"/></svg></span><span class="timeline-year">1990er</span></div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Erste Wettkampferfolge</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">DUC-Mitglieder nehmen erfolgreich an regionalen und nationalen Wettkämpfen im Flossenschwimmen teil.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item fade-in">
                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-header"><span class="timeline-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4" fill="#FFD400" stroke="#FFD400"/><path d="M12 3v2M12 19v2M3 12h2M19 12h2"/></svg></span><span class="timeline-year">2000er</span></div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Ausbau der Ausbildung</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">Das Ausbildungsangebot wird erweitert. Neben klassischem Gerätetauchen kommen Apnoe- und Freediving-Kurse hinzu.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item fade-in">
                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-header"><span class="timeline-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FFD400" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="1.5"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg></span><span class="timeline-year">2010er</span></div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Landesleistungsstützpunkt</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">Der DUC Essen wird offizieller Landesleistungsstützpunkt und etabliert sich als führender Verein für Apnoe-Sport in NRW.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item fade-in">
                <div class="timeline-card timeline-highlight">
                    <div class="timeline-header"><span class="timeline-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FFD400" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M12 14v8"/><path d="M8 22h8"/><path d="M9 6l3 3 3-3" stroke="#004F9E" fill="none" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span><span class="timeline-year">18. Mai 2025</span></div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Deutsche Meisterschaften Apnoe</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">
                        <strong>Jennifer Wendland</strong> holt zwei Goldmedaillen:<br>
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="#FFD400" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="1.5" style="vertical-align: middle;"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M12 14v8"/><path d="M8 22h8"/></svg> Speed-Endurance 8×50m (05:54,80)<br>
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="#FFD400" stroke="#004F9E" stroke-width="1.5" style="vertical-align: middle;"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M12 14v8"/><path d="M8 22h8"/></svg> Speed-Endurance 4×50m (02:14,59) <span style="background: var(--blue); color: white; padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">DR</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
